job_description: We are looking for a skilled factory worker or engineer to join our team at GE Appliances. The ideal candidate should have experience with manufacturing processes, equipment maintenance, quality control, safety protocols, and working in a fast-paced production environment.
questions: Walk me through your experience with preventative maintenance on industrial equipment?
Describe a time you identified and resolved a problem with manufacturing equipment?
How do you prioritize tasks in a fast-paced production environment?
Explain your experience with quality control procedures and ensuring product standards?
Can you detail your understanding of factory safety protocols and hazard identification?
